## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d16bd-268">在过程中，将使用此属性 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 来确定是否将原始值或当前值用于某个参数值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d16bd-268">This property is used by the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> during the <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to determine whether the original or current value is used for a parameter value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d16bd-269">这将允许更新主键。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d16bd-269">This lets primary keys be updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d16bd-270">此属性设置为 <xref:System.Data.DataRow> <xref:System.Data.DataRow.Item%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 属性 (<xref:System.Data.DataRow> 索引器) 或对象的方法所使用 <xref:System.Data.DataRow.GetChildRows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Data.DataRow> 的的版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d16bd-270">This property is set to the version of the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> used by the <xref:System.Data.DataRow.Item%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property (<xref:System.Data.DataRow> indexer), or the <xref:System.Data.DataRow.GetChildRows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method of the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> object.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d16bd-271">下面的示例创建 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> 并设置其一些属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d16bd-271">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter("pDName", OracleType.VarChar)  
